*** To add a new source ***

-> Create constants in SourcesConstants
    - base url
    - edito url
    - section names
    - name
    - source object and add to the source list

-> Add logo and mini logo to drawables

-> Add source color and button colors in colors.xml

-> Add mini logo, logo, background color and button link color in SourceUtils switch

-> Update filters binding in array // TODO to update for multinationales

-> Update filter_layout_sources

-> Create retrofit request, koin module

-> Create network models

-> Create network repo

-> Implement in fetch switch (rss, categories and source pages)

-> Write needed test(Unit & Instrumented)
